				Hello everyone! <br>  <br> I was just wondering if anyone knew what VI plans to do on the Firiona Vie Server in regards to the introduction of the SoL expansion. I know many people will want to play a Vah Shir &quot;just to try it out&quot; like what happened to the iksar after RoK was introduced. Does this mean that for a time FV will be even lower in population, or will we get a chance to have two characters(one normal, the other Vah Shir?) <br>  <br> Frankly, I'm really in favor of the one character limit, but on the other hand.... It's going to hurt FV if too many people leave and decide not to come back. I honestly want to know if there is a good solution to this issue? Any ideas?		

